title Luồng 1 - Giám sát và báo cáo: Xuất CSV (GET export)

== Luồng 1 - Giám sát và báo cáo ==

actor Admin
participant "AdminSystemReportController" as Ctrl
participant "SystemReportDAO" as DAO
database "Database" as DB

Admin -> Ctrl: GET action=export, from, to
Ctrl -> Ctrl: auth admin
Ctrl -> DAO: getDailyReport(...)
DAO -> DB
DB --> DAO
DAO --> Ctrl
Ctrl -> Ctrl: set headers CSV
Ctrl -> Admin: body file CSV

